      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency throughout the powerband. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true, equipped with refreshed bushings and dampers that preserve the chassis's legendary communicative feedback. A driver-focused machine with all major mechanical points addressed.",
